{"tid":2426280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港抗爭布條高雄展出 陳其邁撐場","createTime":"2021-02-28T03:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T04:04:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07b77236a5f141862c40525cb48a5bd2c99fe32d","tid":2426280,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:51:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/ENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2FENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M%2F&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3jsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=9d062432\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210228%2FENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M%2F&h=64d29a76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210228/ENXJUH5AKJDRBAENURFRDRBV7M/</a><br />\n<br />\n港抗爭布條高雄展出 陳其邁撐場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jSp8NqE019t8ywlNYEKXwO0Jdzk=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HOO2KMMRBJHBRAUYIH2MXLNAO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjSp8NqE019t8ywlNYEKXwO0Jdzk%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHOO2KMMRBJHBRAUYIH2MXLNAO4.jpg&h=705f72d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■高雄有展覽完整展出反送中運動長達40公尺的的示威布條，陳其邁到場參觀。<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動將滿兩周年，高雄駁二藝術特區推出「若水，如火，有聲：一個關於行動的展覽」及「返校Detention實境體驗展」。高雄市長陳其邁昨日特意前來參觀，並表示「這兩個展，一個是敍述香港爭取自由民主的現在式，一個則以實演方式呈現台灣過去白色恐怖歷史，都呈現了自由民主的價值。」陳更在連儂牆寫下「KH撐HK、香港加油」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「敍述港人不屈不撓」<br />\n<br />\n「一個關於行動的展覽」展出了抗爭現場、新聞攝影、藝術創作到出版紀錄等港台創作逾百件作品，更首次完整展開當時長40公尺的抗爭布條，陳其邁表示，有關展覽是在敍述港人爭取自由，他們不屈不撓的抗爭，但是也面臨包括國安法，或者是其他對香港人權自由的打壓。<br />\n<br />\n展覽現場完整呈現來自香港反送中運動現場的40公尺大型布條，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eqL8iU_J7Js3d6ClUAqVKO6ljy0=/886x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JTWJBCO54ZD37BOA5TWF5JCVNM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeqL8iU_J7Js3d6ClUAqVKO6ljy0%3D%2F886x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJTWJBCO54ZD37BOA5TWF5JCVNM.jpg&h=f1b98099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■展覽展出抗爭者雕像等逾百件作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8fBi8vm03mxtvd7Wg8tnti0VZ6k=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3A62N2MLERFPTFUTUTGPXZFJNA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8fBi8vm03mxtvd7Wg8tnti0VZ6k%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3A62N2MLERFPTFUTUTGPXZFJNA.jpg&h=ed13d7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳其邁留字，亦籲高雄人珍惜得來不易的民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Tun-RPl8cnPgrWUVjAO5v2XyCDI=/1050x591/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6MKSZPNNSBEPHICRK6ODEJMHCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTun-RPl8cnPgrWUVjAO5v2XyCDI%3D%2F1050x591%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6MKSZPNNSBEPHICRK6ODEJMHCY.jpg&h=4eeaa8c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳其邁以便利貼寫下「KH撐HK、香港加油」，貼於展覽連儂牆。"},{"pid":"594da2edaa2cc45f35d8a048fb70091b7a33097c","tid":2426280,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"另一方面<br />\n一直有五毛帶風向<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyr2XZP.png&amp;h=edb9a164&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\nBBBBBBBBBBBBBB<br />\nP牌五毛 最近無咗個P<br />\n留意五毛新風向 分化香港同台灣追擊蔡英文<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-五毛post懶人線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n分化港台post<br />\n台狗,我屌